title: Week 12 NFL Preview, Joel Klatt Interview & College Picks
itunes:title: Week 12 NFL Preview, Joel Klatt Interview & College Picks
description:
DJ and Bucky preview the Week 12 NFL schedule (2:11), FOX College Football lead analyst Joel Klatt joins the show (18:25) to breakdown the Michigan-Ohio State he’ll call on Saturday, plus they discuss Kyler Murray & Will Grier and how they compare to Baker Mayfield (25:20). The guys end the show with their college picks for Rivalry Week (35:00).
